<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="border-n">border <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'bɔːdə(r)/    美 /bɔːrdər/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>边；边缘：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>His handkerchief has a white border. 
他的手帕有一条白边。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>国界；边界；边境（地区）：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>on the border</strong> 
在边境上</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>across / over the border</strong> 
越过边境</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>cross the border</strong> 
穿越边境</p></div></div>